<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="d864e3b4-988f-4ee2-b5f4-dd1aefa20d2b" >

    <h3>Diversity</h3> 
<p>We value and respect diversity of knowledge, worldviews and experiences that come from membership in different groups, and the contribution that diversity makes to the learning, teaching, research and work environment.&nbsp;</p>
    





